      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>Allows you to transform OCIO spaces on-the-fly without having to preconvert textures.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"06b2afd4-2545-453a-bb79-e82511e76989\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><p class=\"title\">Warning</p><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Pre-converting textures is recommended as converting to a new color space at render time is expensive.</p></div></div><h3 id=\"PxrColorSpace-InputColor\">Input Color</h3><p>Texture input to be transformed </p><h3 id=\"PxrColorSpace-ColorSpace\">ColorSpace</h3><p>OCIO convert from specified colorspace to scene-linear</p>"
    }
